name: Smolest Seascape
description: Smol version of my photograph back from 2018 somewhere between Paxos and Antipaxos isl. As an islander my access to the sea is very easy. Many families on my island have small boats that are very useful when you live on an island. Sometimes we take them and go for exploration or fishing. This is one of those times where we return from a fishing day. 16x16px George Angelis 2021.
